org.llrp.ltk.generated.messages

Class GET_READER_CAPABILITIES

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.llrp.ltk.types.LLRPMessage
      • org.llrp.ltk.generated.messages.GET_READER_CAPABILITIES

  • public class GET_READER_CAPABILITIES
extends LLRPMessage
    This message is sent from the Client to the Reader. The Client is able to request only a subset or all the capabilities from the Reader. See also LLRP Specification Section 9.1.1 and LLRP Specification Section 16.1.1
